145
00:09:59,405 --> 00:10:01,805
Alright. I'll do as my wife says.

146
00:10:03,845 --> 00:10:05,125
By the way,

147
00:10:05,205 --> 00:10:07,325
was production of <i>Frosty Moon</i> cancelled

148
00:10:07,845 --> 00:10:10,405
and Lu Di blacklisted because of you?

149
00:10:10,725 --> 00:10:12,125
