260
00:18:04,605 --> 00:18:05,605
Tell us what's going on.

261
00:18:05,685 --> 00:18:07,405
How long have you been together?

262
00:18:07,485 --> 00:18:09,165
Can you share your love story with us?

263
00:18:09,245 --> 00:18:11,605
Aren't you all here
for the product launch event?

264
00:18:11,965 --> 00:18:15,245
Maybe you should be more concerned
about the product instead of gossip.

265
00:18:16,125 --> 00:18:18,125
How about this?
I'm currently working on a new film.

266
00:18:18,405 --> 00:18:20,285
If you'd like to hear more about it,
follow me.

267
00:18:21,405 --> 00:18:23,005
Is it still in the filming process?

268
00:18:23,365 --> 00:18:25,005
We're ready to wrap things up.

269
00:18:25,725 --> 00:18:27,365
There are others that are more suitable.

270
00:18:27,765 --> 00:18:29,245
No way. You deserve it.

271
00:18:29,325 --> 00:18:30,325
Cheers to you.

272
00:18:41,845 --> 00:18:42,685
Xia Lin.

273
00:18:45,645 --> 00:18:48,165
It's you.
I thought I got the wrong person.

274
00:18:48,405 --> 00:18:49,725
Nan? What a coincidence!

275
00:18:49,925 --> 00:18:51,325
What are you doing here?

276
00:18:51,405 --> 00:18:52,805
Our company received an invitation.

277
00:18:52,885 --> 00:18:54,205
I'm here to make up the numbers.

278
00:18:56,445 --> 00:18:57,325
You look beautiful.

279
00:18:59,445 --> 00:19:00,325
Thank you.

280
00:19:01,405 --> 00:19:03,405
Why are you alone?

281
00:19:04,325 --> 00:19:07,085
It's my first time at this kind of event.
I'm not quite used to it.

282
00:19:07,405 --> 00:19:08,885
Thankfully, I ran into you.

283
00:19:10,365 --> 00:19:13,405
To be honest, I'm also trying
to get away from people.

284
00:19:18,245 --> 00:19:19,085
Miss Xia.

285
00:19:21,085 --> 00:19:23,245
You should talk. I'll go walk around.

286
00:19:25,645 --> 00:19:26,845
Allow me to introduce you.

287
00:19:27,365 --> 00:19:29,805
This is Director Jiang
of MeiLai Greater China.

288
00:19:30,605 --> 00:19:31,605
Nice to meet you.

289
00:19:31,685 --> 00:19:34,045
Chu Yan, what have you been up to lately?

290
00:19:34,125 --> 00:19:36,205
I'm sorry. Please excuse me.

291
00:19:36,285 --> 00:19:37,125
Alright.

292
00:19:38,325 --> 00:19:40,165
Thank you for your compliments,
Director Jiang.

293
00:19:40,245 --> 00:19:42,245
Yizhou never compliments me on my looks.

294
00:19:42,725 --> 00:19:44,085
He doesn't care about such things.

295
00:19:44,605 --> 00:19:46,125
I've met Director Ling a few times,

296
00:19:46,565 --> 00:19:48,925
but I've never had the chance
to chat with him.

297
00:19:50,085 --> 00:19:51,205
I'll fix that.

298
00:19:51,285 --> 00:19:52,405
Come visit me next time.

299
00:19:52,485 --> 00:19:55,285
Would Miss Xia and Director Ling
do us the honor of joining us?

300
00:19:56,245 --> 00:19:58,085
I'm sorry, I...

301
00:19:58,165 --> 00:19:59,645
There you are.

302
00:20:01,525 --> 00:20:02,445
Mr. Chu is here, too.

303
00:20:03,765 --> 00:20:04,925
I have to be here.

304
00:20:05,365 --> 00:20:06,445
Ling instructed me

305
00:20:06,765 --> 00:20:10,085
to stay close to his girlfriend.

306
00:20:10,405 --> 00:20:11,845
In case she gets bullied by others.

307
00:20:12,805 --> 00:20:16,925
Miss Xia has Mr. Chu and Director Ling
watching her back.

308
00:20:17,525 --> 00:20:18,885
No need to worry.

309
00:20:19,925 --> 00:20:23,885
I'd like to ask Miss Xia to be
spokesperson for our company.

310
00:20:23,965 --> 00:20:25,485
Would you be interested, Miss Xia?

311
00:20:27,605 --> 00:20:29,165
Thank you for offering, Director Jiang.

312
00:20:29,805 --> 00:20:33,245
But I don't think I'm qualified enough
for such an important job yet.

313
00:20:33,325 --> 00:20:35,805
When I am ready,

314
00:20:36,045 --> 00:20:38,365
I hope Director Jiang
will give me the opportunity.

315
00:20:38,445 --> 00:20:39,925
As long as Miss Xia is willing,

316
00:20:40,005 --> 00:20:41,085
my door is always open.

317
00:20:41,165 --> 00:20:44,685
I'll show her around now.
Please excuse us.

318
00:20:46,125 --> 00:20:48,565
It was nice meeting you both,
Director Xu and Director Jiang.

319
00:20:48,645 --> 00:20:49,645
You too.

320
00:20:55,565 --> 00:20:57,445
I've underestimated you.

321
00:20:58,045 --> 00:21:00,005
Who was that man
chatting with you just now?

322
00:21:00,525 --> 00:21:02,685
Why should I tell you?
How is this your business?

323
00:21:03,325 --> 00:21:04,605
How is it my business?

324
00:21:06,085 --> 00:21:07,925
It doesn't have much to do with me,

325
00:21:08,005 --> 00:21:10,885
but it definitely has a lot to do
with someone in my contacts.

326
00:21:10,965 --> 00:21:13,445
Someone called Ling Yizhou.

327
00:21:16,045 --> 00:21:17,085
What's going on?

328
00:21:18,765 --> 00:21:21,645
I suddenly can't breathe.

329
00:21:22,165 --> 00:21:25,885
Just hearing his name makes you dizzy?

330
00:21:26,285 --> 00:21:28,125
Let me snap some photos
and send them to him.

331
00:21:28,205 --> 00:21:30,245
Stop fooling around.
I'm really not feeling well.

332
00:21:33,125 --> 00:21:34,005
Are you serious?

333
00:21:34,885 --> 00:21:36,245
Should I take you to the hospital?

334
00:21:36,325 --> 00:21:39,245
No. I probably haven't been
getting enough rest.

335
00:21:39,565 --> 00:21:42,445
I'm tired from the event.
I'll be fine after I get some rest.

336
00:21:43,205 --> 00:21:44,285
Let me escort you back.

337
00:21:45,045 --> 00:21:47,645
By the way,
don't mention a word to Ling Yizhou.

338
00:21:48,125 --> 00:21:49,965
Don't worry. Do I look like a snitch?

339
00:21:52,925 --> 00:21:56,525
If reporters get a photo of us,
we'll be in the gossip column again.

340
00:21:57,285 --> 00:21:58,685
Why are you so dumb?

341
00:21:58,765 --> 00:22:00,325
You keep getting hurt again and again.

342
00:22:00,405 --> 00:22:01,565
Why do you love to nag?

343
00:22:01,645 --> 00:22:02,765
You think I like to nag?

344
00:22:03,205 --> 00:22:04,045
What if...

345
00:22:09,485 --> 00:22:11,365
I was very ill before.

346
00:22:11,445 --> 00:22:14,125
He's not just my legal husband.
He saved my life.

347
00:22:30,525 --> 00:22:31,365
Xia Lin?

348
00:22:41,085 --> 00:22:42,365
Long time no see.

349
00:22:48,125 --> 00:22:49,205
Why are you here?

350
00:22:49,965 --> 00:22:54,285
Why are you being so cold
towards an old neighbor?

351
00:22:55,445 --> 00:22:56,685
I don't want to talk to you.

352
00:22:58,085 --> 00:22:59,725
Aren't you curious about when I got back?

353
00:22:59,805 --> 00:23:00,725
Not at all.

354
00:23:01,165 --> 00:23:03,165
You must be here for your girlfriend.

355
00:23:10,445 --> 00:23:11,445
What are you implying?

356
00:23:12,365 --> 00:23:14,085
I just want to inform you out of goodwill.

357
00:23:14,845 --> 00:23:16,085
I saw Chu Yan

358
00:23:16,565 --> 00:23:19,605
and your girlfriend
walk into a hotel room.

359
00:23:36,765 --> 00:23:37,605
You're awake?

360
00:23:38,405 --> 00:23:40,125
Sit down. I'll get you a glass of water.

361
00:23:40,365 --> 00:23:41,205
Sure.

362
00:23:50,765 --> 00:23:52,725
Ling, you're finally here.

363
00:23:53,765 --> 00:23:55,565
I don't have to take care
of your wife anymore.

364
00:23:56,885 --> 00:23:58,005
What's going on, Mumu?

365
00:23:58,085 --> 00:23:59,565
She's not feeling--

366
00:23:59,645 --> 00:24:00,965
I missed you so much, Yizhou.

367
00:24:06,725 --> 00:24:08,685
Alright. You carry on then.

368
00:24:09,245 --> 00:24:10,085
I'll get going.

369
00:24:25,325 --> 00:24:27,285
Miss Jia. I've been waiting for you.

370
00:24:27,765 --> 00:24:29,165
Why were you waiting for me?

371
00:24:30,005 --> 00:24:32,485
My boss is here.
Please don't disturb them.

372
00:24:33,645 --> 00:24:35,405
That's nice of you.

373
00:24:36,445 --> 00:24:37,285
What do you mean?

374
00:24:39,005 --> 00:24:40,885
Your attitude towards your boss.

375
00:24:42,285 --> 00:24:44,245
Never mind.

376
00:24:49,605 --> 00:24:50,685
What about my boss?

377
00:24:51,325 --> 00:24:52,445
I bought too much supper.

378
00:24:53,125 --> 00:24:53,965
Want to share?

379
00:25:07,565 --> 00:25:08,405
Yizhou.

380
00:25:15,645 --> 00:25:16,485
Hubby.

381
00:25:17,085 --> 00:25:18,285
Why are you ignoring me?

382
00:25:22,285 --> 00:25:25,605
You're being too nice to me.
Usually that means something's wrong.

383
00:25:30,845 --> 00:25:32,165
When I finish my work here,

384
00:25:33,045 --> 00:25:35,045
can I stay for a few more days?

385
00:25:35,725 --> 00:25:38,285
Have you forgotten
you have a family to attend to now?

386
00:25:39,285 --> 00:25:40,765
You are my family.

387
00:25:41,565 --> 00:25:45,045
Dear Mr. Ling, would you have time
to take me on a date?

388
00:25:51,125 --> 00:25:52,045
Time isn't the problem.

389
00:25:52,805 --> 00:25:54,405
It's your sincerity that matters.

390
00:25:56,605 --> 00:25:58,205
If you won't promise me, don't touch me.

391
00:26:01,365 --> 00:26:02,725
Fine. I promise.

392
00:26:05,205 --> 00:26:07,685
Go take a shower.

393
00:26:11,605 --> 00:26:12,525
Wait here.

394
00:26:26,725 --> 00:26:27,845
What's wrong with me?

395
00:26:29,605 --> 00:26:30,445
It can't be...

396
00:26:31,565 --> 00:26:33,765
Is there something wrong with my heart?

397
00:26:35,725 --> 00:26:36,725
It can't be.

398
00:27:14,925 --> 00:27:17,045
DATE PLAN

399
00:27:26,645 --> 00:27:28,685
<i>Cancel my meeting tomorrow.</i>

400
00:27:48,405 --> 00:27:50,885
Don't move. Mine.

401
00:28:15,845 --> 00:28:17,565
Why are you touching my hair?

402
00:28:21,005 --> 00:28:21,965
Why are you holding me?

403
00:28:25,845 --> 00:28:27,645
I fell asleep. How would I know?

404
00:28:27,885 --> 00:28:29,405
Why are you on my bed?

405
00:28:30,645 --> 00:28:32,605
You're the one who invited me in.

406
00:28:49,765 --> 00:28:50,925
What do you think of this?

407
00:28:52,005 --> 00:28:53,045
Are you buying it for me?

408
00:28:53,845 --> 00:28:56,405
We are on a date, not in a meeting.

409
00:28:56,765 --> 00:28:59,205
You're always in a suit.
I look like your secretary.

410
00:29:00,925 --> 00:29:04,045
Mumu, this shirt doesn't suit me.
It's for children.

411
00:29:05,005 --> 00:29:06,765
It will suit you as long as it fits.

412
00:29:07,325 --> 00:29:09,365
Besides, you lack youthful spirit.

413
00:29:10,165 --> 00:29:11,005
Go, try it on.

414
00:29:11,085 --> 00:29:13,485
Go now.

415
00:29:39,685 --> 00:29:41,845
Hey you, do you have a girlfriend?

416
00:29:42,485 --> 00:29:43,605
Can we be friends on WeChat?

417
00:29:44,565 --> 00:29:46,085
I'm sorry, miss.

418
00:29:47,245 --> 00:29:48,925
I already have a wife.

419
00:29:51,885 --> 00:29:54,165
Why are you being so nice today?

420
00:29:54,245 --> 00:29:55,405
When am I not nice?

421
00:29:56,205 --> 00:29:59,325
You're buying me stuff when you're
out shopping. I feel very touched.

422
00:30:01,965 --> 00:30:04,285
Bend your head
so I can remove the price tag.

423
00:30:07,965 --> 00:30:08,805
What are you doing?

424
00:30:08,885 --> 00:30:11,725
Put me down. We're in a changing room.
We'll get in trouble.

425
00:30:11,805 --> 00:30:12,845
What kind of trouble?

426
00:30:13,125 --> 00:30:15,885
Didn't you want to remove my tag?
I'll put you down when you're done.

427
00:31:20,685 --> 00:31:22,685
When I dropped Feifei off
at the airport yesterday,

428
00:31:22,765 --> 00:31:24,525
she seemed to have something on her mind.

429
00:31:25,005 --> 00:31:28,245
She always boasts that nothing
gets to her. What could it be?

430
00:31:29,365 --> 00:31:30,965
Maybe I'm being too sensitive.

431
00:31:35,245 --> 00:31:36,925
What's wrong? Are you not feeling well?

432
00:31:37,005 --> 00:31:40,565
My chest has been feeling tight lately.
I often can't breathe.

433
00:31:42,365 --> 00:31:44,925
Once we're back home,
let's get you scheduled for a checkup.

434
00:31:46,125 --> 00:31:47,005
By the way,

435
00:31:47,085 --> 00:31:49,045
don't tell Mr. Ling about this.

436
00:31:49,125 --> 00:31:50,765
He'll make a mountain out of a molehill.

437
00:31:50,845 --> 00:31:51,685
Got it.

438
00:31:52,885 --> 00:31:54,965
But before I left,

439
00:31:55,405 --> 00:31:58,525
Mr. Ling was mad about something.

440
00:31:58,805 --> 00:32:02,125
That's nothing compared to being
seen together by the reporters.

441
00:32:02,405 --> 00:32:03,405
You're right. Let's hurry.

442
00:32:04,205 --> 00:32:06,965
Miss Xia, we heard Director Ling
rescheduled his plans to come see you.

443
00:32:07,045 --> 00:32:08,325
Make way.

444
00:32:09,285 --> 00:32:10,205
Please, let us through.

445
00:32:11,485 --> 00:32:12,325
Miss Xia.

446
00:32:12,605 --> 00:32:15,285
Miss Xia, please comment on the matter.

447
00:32:36,685 --> 00:32:40,525
Could it be a relapse?

448
00:32:42,085 --> 00:32:46,405
Doctor, I've been experiencing
palpitations, chest pain, and fatigue.

449
00:32:46,925 --> 00:32:49,405
Is there something wrong with me?

450
00:32:50,525 --> 00:32:51,605
Don't worry.

451
00:32:51,885 --> 00:32:55,005
Based on your medical report,
you have severe anemia.

452
00:32:55,725 --> 00:32:57,605
Have you had similar symptoms before?

453
00:32:57,925 --> 00:33:00,765
I used to have leukemia.
You were my doctor.

454
00:33:03,005 --> 00:33:04,965
I don't remember
performing surgery on you.

455
00:33:06,125 --> 00:33:09,005
I had my checkup at this hospital.

456
00:33:09,285 --> 00:33:11,685
I was diagnosed and had surgery
at a private hospital.

457
00:33:12,205 --> 00:33:15,805
Bring me your diagnosis and surgery report
so I can have a look.

458
00:33:16,365 --> 00:33:17,205
Sure.

459
00:34:01,325 --> 00:34:02,965
I didn't even hear you. You scared me!

460
00:34:03,205 --> 00:34:04,045
What are you doing?

461
00:34:04,485 --> 00:34:06,845
I found a safe at home and got curious.

462
00:34:46,724 --> 00:34:47,925
Hello?

463
00:34:49,724 --> 00:34:50,565
<i>Hello, Mumu.</i>

464
00:34:59,845 --> 00:35:00,845
Mumu, what's wrong?

465
00:35:03,485 --> 00:35:05,725
GANGDONG MUNICIPAL HOSPITAL
BLOOD TEST REPORT

466
00:35:06,005 --> 00:35:06,845
Hello?

467
00:35:17,245 --> 00:35:18,885
Mumu, say something! Hello?

468
00:35:21,045 --> 00:35:21,885
<i>Hello?</i>

469
00:35:22,325 --> 00:35:23,165
<i>Mumu.</i>

470
00:35:23,765 --> 00:35:24,605
<i>Mumu.</i>

471
00:35:26,085 --> 00:35:27,125
<i>Mumu, talk to me!</i>

472
00:35:40,165 --> 00:35:41,885
BLOOD SAMPLE RESULTS: NORMAL

473
00:35:44,685 --> 00:35:46,765
DIAGNOSIS: ANEMIA

474
00:36:00,285 --> 00:36:02,205
DIAGNOSIS: ANEMIA

475
00:36:26,445 --> 00:36:28,605
Mumu, why is it so dark in here?

476
00:36:29,645 --> 00:36:30,685
It doesn't matter.

477
00:36:39,645 --> 00:36:40,485
Mumu...

478
00:36:41,085 --> 00:36:43,045
This report says
that I don't have leukemia.

479
00:36:44,205 --> 00:36:46,005
Why was it in your safe?

480
00:36:55,565 --> 00:36:56,605
You found everything?

481
00:36:57,445 --> 00:37:01,645
Yes. Things I should have seen,
things I shouldn't have seen,

482
00:37:01,885 --> 00:37:03,365
I found it all.

483
00:37:06,765 --> 00:37:07,605
Mumu.

484
00:37:08,525 --> 00:37:10,245
I'll tell you whatever you want to know.

485
00:37:10,325 --> 00:37:13,045
Please don't let
your imagination run wild, OK?

486
00:37:16,325 --> 00:37:19,005
Start talking. I want to hear the truth.

487
00:37:27,605 --> 00:37:31,085
The private hospital where you got
your diagnosis is owned by our family.

488
00:37:33,405 --> 00:37:35,285
I replaced your original diagnosis report,

489
00:37:35,965 --> 00:37:38,605
and falsified the information
that I was a bone marrow match for you.

490
00:37:41,045 --> 00:37:42,445
I knew you would come look for me.

491
00:37:50,725 --> 00:37:52,765
I know this sounds unreasonable
to you now.

492
00:37:52,845 --> 00:37:55,805
But if I hadn't done so,
we would miss our chance with each other.

493
00:37:56,765 --> 00:37:59,525
So you arranged
this bone marrow donation act

494
00:37:59,605 --> 00:38:01,165
and waited for me to knock on your door?

495
00:38:01,885 --> 00:38:04,725
How long were you planning
to hide this from me

496
00:38:06,005 --> 00:38:08,565
Until you trusted me completely.

497
00:38:09,245 --> 00:38:11,045
You want me to trust a liar?

498
00:38:13,605 --> 00:38:14,805
Don't you find that ironic?

499
00:38:16,525 --> 00:38:18,685
But we're together now and I love you.

500
00:38:20,045 --> 00:38:21,245
I'm scared of your love.

501
00:38:22,165 --> 00:38:23,365
You hate An Ran,

502
00:38:23,445 --> 00:38:26,205
but how are you different from her?

503
00:38:27,205 --> 00:38:28,485
I never meant to hurt you!

504
00:38:28,925 --> 00:38:30,165
You hurt me mentally.

505
00:38:30,405 --> 00:38:32,045
Did you ever consider my feelings?

506
00:38:32,325 --> 00:38:33,805
I was only 21 years old.

507
00:38:33,885 --> 00:38:36,605
Fresh out of college with a bright future
ahead. Then a death sentence.

508
00:38:37,085 --> 00:38:38,525
You only thought about what you want.

509
00:38:38,605 --> 00:38:41,405
Do you know how much pain
I suffered back then?

510
00:38:42,005 --> 00:38:44,005
If it's a happy ending,
does the process matter?

511
00:38:44,085 --> 00:38:45,325
Isn't it important, Ling Yizhou?

512
00:38:46,125 --> 00:38:47,165
What am I to you?

513
00:38:47,645 --> 00:38:51,445
A puppet for you to manipulate?
A pet for your amusement?

514
00:38:57,285 --> 00:38:59,085
You've seen how I treat you.

515
00:39:00,845 --> 00:39:03,085
I've always wanted
to give you a grand wedding.

516
00:39:03,165 --> 00:39:06,165
I've always wanted to announce
to the world that you are my wife.

517
00:39:06,645 --> 00:39:07,805
What about you?

518
00:39:07,885 --> 00:39:10,205
You keep running and hiding.
Have you given me a chance?

519
00:39:10,645 --> 00:39:12,925
I keep breaking my own boundaries for you.

520
00:39:13,485 --> 00:39:14,565
Yet now you ask me...

521
00:39:15,645 --> 00:39:17,045
what you are to me.

522
00:39:17,405 --> 00:39:19,005
What do you think you are to me?

523
00:39:19,245 --> 00:39:21,325
I only ask for honesty and respect.

524
00:39:21,725 --> 00:39:24,005
No surveillance, no shadowing, no lies.

525
00:39:38,965 --> 00:39:40,405
If I could start over again...

526
00:39:42,005 --> 00:39:43,165
I would do the same thing.

527
00:39:50,005 --> 00:39:51,525
I'm very disappointed with you.

528
00:40:02,325 --> 00:40:03,165
Mumu!

529
00:40:10,045 --> 00:40:10,885
Hello.

530
00:40:12,325 --> 00:40:13,285
Where are you?

531
00:40:13,365 --> 00:40:14,485
<i>I'm at home.</i>

532
00:40:14,885 --> 00:40:18,045
<i>I just watched a romantic movie.</i>

533
00:40:18,325 --> 00:40:19,605
You're finished filming?

534
00:40:21,165 --> 00:40:22,285
<i>In the movie,</i>

535
00:40:22,565 --> 00:40:26,445
<i>the couple said three words</i>
<i>to each other before they parted.</i>

536
00:40:27,285 --> 00:40:28,205
<i>Guess what they said.</i>

537
00:40:30,005 --> 00:40:31,325
What do I get if I get it right?

538
00:40:31,685 --> 00:40:33,725
<i>I'll definitely satisfy you, alright?</i>

539
00:40:36,045 --> 00:40:36,885
Mumu.

540
00:40:37,285 --> 00:40:38,365
<i>Just say it.</i>

541
00:40:40,685 --> 00:40:43,965
I love you.

542
00:40:47,005 --> 00:40:48,005
-Director Ling.
-Sir.

543
00:40:55,365 --> 00:40:57,565
Thank you, everyone.
Let's continue with our meeting.

544
00:42:25,765 --> 00:42:27,525
Subtitle translation by Alice Hsing

545
00:42:27,765 --> 00:42:30,725
Mr. Ling just wants you
to get some rest at home.

546
00:42:30,805 --> 00:42:32,525
Ling Yizhou, you love being in control.

547
00:42:33,165 --> 00:42:34,805
Even in love, you try to set people up.

548
00:42:35,165 --> 00:42:36,605
I was just trying to protect you.

549
00:42:36,685 --> 00:42:37,965
I'm not your pet.

550
00:42:38,165 --> 00:42:39,845
I can survive
without you taking care of me.

551
00:42:41,005 --> 00:42:42,605
I won't let you go.

552
00:42:42,965 --> 00:42:44,525
I never thought about getting a divorce.

553
00:42:44,605 --> 00:42:46,765
I just wanted some time
to think about our relationship.

554
00:42:47,125 --> 00:42:49,085
I never thought you would lock me up.
